thread.title: Denisa Cifrikova

author: Denisa Cifrikova
title: Denisa Cifrikova
text: I needed some invitations for my daughter's upcoming 6th birthday. I checked two different companies. Optimalprint came up slightly more expensive, but their delivery times were very quick compared to the other company. I went with Optimalprint. The order arrived swiftly within days, the quality was great and I was very pleased with the look of the invites themselves. They also sent 4 spare invites which was greatly appreciated.
